oina Precup @ ArXiv, 2020.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"full\",\"id\":110,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-large\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2008.08844\"><img src=\"http://localhost/homepage/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/GFN-1024x574.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-110\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6} -->\n<h6><strong><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2008.08844\"><em>Complete the Missing Half: Augmenting Aggregation Filtering with Diversification forGraph Convolutional Networks</em></a></strong></h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sitao Luan<span class=\"has-inline-color has-accent-color\"><strong>*</strong></span>, <strong>Mingde Zhao<span class=\"has-inline-color has-accent-color\">*</span></strong>, Chenqing Hua<strong><span class=\"has-inline-color has-accent-color\">*</span></strong>, Xiao-Wen Chang, Doina Precup @ ArXiv, 2020.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"full\",\"id\":160,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/homepage/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/TAIA-1024x495.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-160\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6} -->\n<h6><strong><a href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/9207176\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/9207176\"><em>TWO-STAGE AUTOMATIC IMAGE ANNOTATION BASED ON LATENT SEMANTIC SCENE CLASSIFICATION</em></a></strong></h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hongwei Ge, Kai Zhang, Yaqing Hou, Chao Yu,&nbsp;<strong>Mingde Zhao</strong>, Zhen Wang, Liang Sun @ Internation